    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Infrastructure of computer science department is good and labs are well equipped with new computer and air-conditioning rooms",
          "name": "Kamlesh Humraj Harinkhede",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The lecture staff is very supportive and informative",
          "name": "Vaibhav Ravishankar Yewale",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The course is completed by the time and for weak students remedial classes are also taken",
          "name": "Vaibhav Ravishankar Yewale",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "All the teachers are very co-operative with all students",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our college is focused on extra curricular activities with studies",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "1. First of all I would like to mention the placement section and and teaching pattern is my one of liked thing in my college",
          "name": "Sangram Suresh Puri",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "2. Second of all I would like to mention about the  teachers and department pattern and their behaviour towards the student",
          "name": "Sangram Suresh Puri",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Food quality is good, and college arranges many sports programs and annual gatherings.",
          "name": "Kuldip Thakre",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sports are actively organized and also sports facilities are good.",
          "name": "Abhishek Hatwar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Parking are mostly covered with car not much space for students vehicles",
          "name": "Kamlesh Humraj Harinkhede",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "WiFi connection is very slow in our department",
          "name": "Kamlesh Humraj Harinkhede",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "College committee can reduce the financial stress of students",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Disliked : 1. First thing in this section which I will say is the course completion,  teachers should be focus on here.",
          "name": "Sangram Suresh Puri",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "2.Second thing which I didn't liked here is the facilities for outer students",
          "name": "Sangram Suresh Puri",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Classrooms for our department are below average.",
